<p>Librsvg now has a development guide, intended for interns and newcomers to the code.  It&rsquo;s available at <a href="https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/librsvg/devel-docs/index.html">https://gnome.pages.gitlab.gnome.org/librsvg/devel-docs/index.html</a></p>
